define({"topics":[{"title":"Searcher","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Each TMS is an extensive and comprehensive tool to manage your translatable content.         As a result, it is very important that it has a <strong class=\"ph b\">good searcher<\/strong> so that you could         easily find what you are looking for.<\/p>","href":"topics\/searcher.html","attributes":{"data-id":"searcher"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"searcher-d571e197","topics":[]},{"title":"Notifications","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">An intelligent TMS should act as a project manager and communicator between team         members, and notify everyone working on it when they have new tasks, and when there is new         content ready for translation. <\/p>","href":"topics\/notifications.html","attributes":{"data-id":"notifications"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"notifications-d571e211","topics":[]},{"title":"Analytics","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">According to <em class=\"ph i\">The Economist,<\/em> data is now the most valuable resource in the         world, ahead of oil. That is why it should be regarded as the company's biggest asset. The         translation process is no different. You should be able to present the management with all         kinds of data at any time.<\/p>","href":"topics\/analytics.html","attributes":{"data-id":"analytics"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"analytics-d571e222","topics":[]},{"title":"Workflows","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">One of the main features of a TMS is <strong class=\"ph b\">work automation<\/strong>. This is reflected, for         example, by workflows which keep all translation stakeholders on the same page. This is         where the process is actually managed with full traceability.<\/p>","href":"topics\/workflows.html","attributes":{"data-id":"workflows"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"workflows-d571e236","topics":[]},{"title":"Working outside","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Often TMSs are based on a subscription model in which you pay for the number of         concurrent users, i.e. people that use the tool at the same time. As a result, it is good if         the TMS offered the possibility for the vendor to work in another CAT tool.<\/p>","href":"topics\/working_outside.html","attributes":{"data-id":"working_outside"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"working_outside-d571e250","topics":[]},{"title":"File formats ","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">You need to know what file formats are usually sent for translation in your company         so that you could decide which TMS to choose.<\/p>","href":"topics\/file_formats.html","attributes":{"data-id":"file_formats"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"file_formats-d571e261","topics":[]},{"title":"Anonymization","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">To comply with the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https:\/\/eur-lex.europa.eu\/eli\/reg\/2016\/679\/oj\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">GDPR<\/a>, companies are required to anonymize clients'         TM content, essentially remove personal data.<\/p>","href":"topics\/anonymization.html","attributes":{"data-id":"anonymization"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"anonymization-d571e272","topics":[]},{"title":"Mobile version","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">The world goes mobile, so do TMSs.<\/p>","href":"topics\/mobile_version.html","attributes":{"data-id":"mobile_version"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"mobile_version-d571e286","topics":[]}]});